\newlabel{tab:samplers}{{2}{23}{The three posterior samplers as members of the unified family \eqref {eq:unified_posterior_drift}. All share the prior drift $\drift ^{\gdiff }_\tau =\fmvel _\tau +\tfrac 12\gdiff _\tau ^2\genscore _\tau $, the likelihood-score correction $\gweight _\tau \,\bar S_\tau $, and the observation-interpolant machinery; they differ only in $\gdiff _\tau $, the weight $\gweight _\tau =\vscoef _\tau +\tfrac 12\gdiff _\tau ^2$, and the source.\relax }{table.caption.27}{}}
